race.comment: GOT A HABIT (6) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 25.27 beating Magic Loki. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. CARRY ON MACI (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 6 last run (25.80) at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Leading player again. SOLITARY FLICKER (8) was a winner two back when leading throughout but drifted back latest and safely held when 7th and beaten 10 lengths at Bendigo (28.73). The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. In the mix. ZIPPING SINGH (7) cannot be left out over a shorter distance.
